POLIOMYELITIS UPDATE (23): GLOBAL (SYRIA, PAKISTAN, DEMOCRATIC REPUBLIC OF THE CONGO) WILD POLIOVIRUS TYPE 1, CIRCULATING VACCINE DERIVED POLIOVIRUS TYPE 2
***********************************************************************************************************************************************************
